  "detailed_description": "<h1>New game released</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>‘Live Empire 2’ is a simulated cultivation game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sign a platform and start live broadcast</h2>Let the anchor enhance his reputation through live broadcast, sign a better platform and gain more profits.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597280/extras/120cdeb905cd96cf93007050372136b8.avif?t=1710139946\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597280/extras/1a1fd00100cd07c64639a69114e762a4.avif?t=1710139946\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cultivate attributes to improve live broadcast effect</h2>Training anchors and improving attributes will play a bonus role in different live broadcasts, making your income from each live broadcast greater!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597280/extras/1aa639b45e86c4e2f98ae43c6d553454.avif?t=1710139946\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enhance goodwill through dating</h2>What should you do after earning money? Of course, it’s a date with your favorite girl. Dating more will improve her goodwill, unlock more dating places and trigger hidden plots. More surprises are waiting for you to discover!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597280/extras/5d92c0dbf9fbcbd6b60d4a91b527465e.avif?t=1710139946\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dressing at will</h2>Another advantage of improving goodwill is that more clothes can be unlocked, which can be changed on the live broadcast or on the date.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597280/extras/72b52bff026c11c6cbd598d31dcdf337.avif?t=1710139946\" width=600 height=338 /></span>",
